## Completeness Checklist

- [ ] Risk ID assigned and unique within the register
- [ ] Title is concise and unambiguous
- [ ] Category correctly selected from allowed values
- [ ] Description explains root cause and context
- [ ] Likelihood score justified by evidence or expert judgement
- [ ] Impact score justified by business or technical consequence
- [ ] Score calculated correctly (L × I)
- [ ] Mitigation plan is actionable and has a named owner
- [ ] Due date set for mitigation completion
- [ ] Status reflects current state
- [ ] Review history updated
